HEADWORD: Unsound
<hw>Un*sound"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not sound; not
whole; not solid; defective; infirm; diseased.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un*sound"ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*sound"ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unspar</ent>⟦br⟧
